  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A comparison of fibrin sealant 2 versus Surgicel® as an addition to standard surgical
      practice in stopping mild to moderate soft tissue bleeding during retroperitoneal or
      intra-abdominal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The time it will take to stop bleeding will be measured and compared between patients who are
      treated with fibrin sealant 2 to those who are treated with Surgicel®.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
